desc_long								关于这款游戏							Spark Rising is a FPS arcade game where you flight back against an endless stream of minions thrown at you from a mad god that is tearing the galaxy asunder.You play as a Spark Bot and you must betray your master god to save what's left before reality is twisted all to hell. The problem is... how do you fight back against a god that can break heaven, earth and hell? Plunder rare crystals and loot to build up enough power to fight back. And perhaps the story might end with you as a hero.Join us in this journey in the creation of Spark Rising!MASSIVE BATTLESEngage in battles with enemies swarming you from all sides! GAMEPLAY FEATURES:Dynamically Changing Arena - No two locations are ever the same as some battle maps are procedurally generated, others are user generatedDestructible Fortresses –  All structures and defenses are completely destructibleUpgrade your Battle Exo-Suits – Gather rare crystals and loot to upgrade your exo-suits to take on a god						
